title: Ep. 47 - This YouTuber Flew 10,000 Miles to be on Our Podcast (ft. I did a thing)
description: This week we are joined by Australian YouTuber "I did a thing" while Nick's on Vacation. The boys cover Amouranth's private jet, meeting a pilot influencer, and how Australians are funnier than everyone else in the world.
